thread.title: Trump Claims Russia Probe Aims to Help Democrats in Midterms

author: Peter Nicholas
title: Trump Claims Russia Probe Aims to Help Democrats in Midterms
text:
Republican President Donald Trump broadened his condemnation of the Russia probe with a tweet Tuesday accusing it of being a partisan exercise that could unfairly tip the midterm elections in favor of Democratic congressional candidates.
The “angry Democrats” who are “working on the rigged Russia Witch Hunt, will be MEDDLING with the mid-term elections,” the president said in his tweet.
